OL,3,CRishi Sunak 'excluded deaf community'
OL,4,Cas he called election
OL,6,FPrime Minister Rishi Sunak has been
OL,7,Faccused of excluding the deaf
OL,8,Fcommunity by not having a sign
OL,9,Flanguage interpreter with him when he
OL,10,Fcalled the General Election.
OL,12,FAccording to the hearing charity RNID,
OL,13,FDowning Street pledged to have British
OL,14,FSign Language (BSL) interpreters on
OL,15,Fhand for big announcements from spring
OL,16,F2024.
OL,18,FHowever, there was no interpreter in
OL,19,Fsight when Mr Sunak made his
OL,20,Fannouncement outside Number 10 on
OL,21,FWednesday afternoon.
