OL,6,FThe charity wrote on X, formerly
OL,7,FTwitter: "Where's the British Sign
OL,8,FLanguage (BSL) interpreter
OL,9,F@10DowningStreet?
OL,11,F"Calling a General Election is one of
OL,12,Fthe biggest moves our country can make
OL,13,F` deaf people deserve to have that
OL,14,Finformation at the same time as
OL,15,Feveryone else. This is not good enough!
OL,17,F"Let this be the last time British
OL,18,FSign Language (BSL) users are left
OL,19,Fbehind ` we call on all candidates to
OL,20,Fmake this the most accessible General
OL,21,FElection ever."
