OL,6,FAs part of the Government's disability
OL,7,Faction plan, officials said they would
OL,8,F"make government publications and
OL,9,Fcommunications more accessible".
OL,11,FThis includes a pledge that "Number 10
OL,12,FDowning Street will work to provide in-
OL,13,Fsitu BSL interpretation for all major
OL,14,Fpress conferences and briefings from
OL,15,Fspring 2024 onwards."
